de.elo.ix.client

Class FindInfoAsInternalSQL

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.elo.ix.client.FindInfoAsInternalSQL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FindInfoAsInternalSQL
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    SQL command that is built from a FindInfo object. This class contains the elements of an internal SQL statement for finding Sord objects. Modifying this elements might cause errors or wrong results in subsequent versions of IX.
    Since:
    9.00.030.029
    See Also:
    IXServerEvents.onBeforeFindSordsInternalSQL(IXServerEventsContext, FindInfo, SordZ, FindInfoAsInternalSQL), Serialized Form
